First Uranium Rises Most in Eight Months as AngloGold Ashanti to Buy Stake

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-22T07:13:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/first-uranium-rises-most-in-eight-months-as-anglogold-ashanti-to-buy-stake.html
First Uranium Corp. (FIU)  surged the most
in eight months as AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. said it would buy a
19.79 percent stake in the uranium producer for about 205
million rand.  The stock rallied 42 cents, or 14 percent, to 3.37 rand by
9:12 a.m. in Johannesburg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  